substep.action:
Parse the YAML output. Store values in session variables:
- {{session.date}}
- {{session.owner}}
- {{session.shared_folder}}
- {{session.team}}
- {{session.git_commit}}, {{session.branch}}, {{session.repository}}

Validate that shared_folder is non-empty and that the path exists on
disk. If shared_folder is missing, halt with a clear error: the user
must run the workflow from inside a thoughts-mapped repo.

substep.output:
Session metadata captured:
- Owner: {{session.owner}}
- Date: {{session.date}}
- Team: {{session.team}}
- Shared folder: {{session.shared_folder}}
- Repository: {{session.repository}} ({{session.branch}} @ {{session.git_commit}})

Proceeding to CONTEXT.md read.
